title: Chicken Spinach Lasagna
directions: Step 2:	Cook noodles as directed on box.
Step 3:	Mix spinach and ricotta together.
Step 4:	Drizzle 1/2 jar Alfredo over bottom of pan.
Step 6:	Spread 1/3 of mix over noodles.
Step 9:	Add 1/2 jar Alfredo and 1 jar 4 cheese sauce.
Step 11:	Top with remaining Alfredo, mozzarella, Parmesan and parsley.
Step 12:	Bake at 350 degrees, covered in foil, for 25 minutes, then remove foil and continue baking for 5 minutes.
ingredients: 30 oz. Food Club Alfredo Pasta Sauce
1 lb. Boneless Chicken Breasts (cooked and shredded)
